    <num value="241">SEC. 241.</num><heading class="uppercase"> Eliminating stigmatizing language relating to substance use.</heading>
    <subsection identifier="/tII/stD/s241/a" id="H455AF579E88449C3AD9848F8DC6A17FA" class="bill-dtd-OLC">
        <num value="a">(a)</num>
        <heading class="titlecase"> Block Grants for Prevention and Treatment of Substance Use.—</heading>
        <chapeau>Part B of title XIX of the Public Health Service Act (<ref href="/us/usc/42/300x">42 U.S.C. 300x et seq.</ref>) is amended—</chapeau>
<page id="page126">H.R. 7666—126</page>
<paragraph identifier="/tII/stD/s241/a/1" id="H4DFB8347DFF7435F87D899C3C58030AC" class="bill-dtd-OLC"><num value="1"><sidenote topic="olrcClassification" role="target" note="CO">42/300x prec</sidenote>(1)</num>
        <content> in the part heading, by striking “<quotedText><inline class="smallCaps"><b>Substance Abuse</b></inline></quotedText>” and inserting “<quotedText><inline class="smallCaps"><b>Substance Use</b></inline></quotedText>”; </content></paragraph>
<paragraph identifier="/tII/stD/s241/a/2" id="HBF1186D755EF4B0EBE2D1E23B6EE34C4" class="bill-dtd-OLC"><num value="2"><sidenote topic="olrcClassification" role="target" note="CO">42/300x-21 prec</sidenote>(2)</num>
        <content> in subpart II, by amending the subpart heading to read as follows: “<quotedText><b>Block grants for substance use prevention, treatment, and recovery services</b></quotedText>”;</content></paragraph>
